Body:
I bought this blender after my wife accidentally dropped our old blender (the 

 Oster 6811 6-Cup Glass Jar 12-Speed Blender, Brushed Nickel
















  ) on the floor and broke it. I should have bought another Oster, as I've been really disappointed by this blender. It claims to have 700 watts of maximum blending power, but it can't do smoothies (which is the only thing I use it for) unless I add a ton of liquid. Also, the top will no longer push down all the way. Really disappointing.
